These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, aconite, lily, balloon-flower
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, malaysian, spanish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, soy-milk, iced-tea
 1. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the spanish is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the malaysian is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
 7. the person who growsrose is the person drinking water##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person drinking water is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
11. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job           | balloon-flower         | aconite    | lily | rose    |
| Nationality   | french        | malaysian | spanish | american   |
| Sport         | soy-milk | coffee   | iced-tea  | water |

