.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, juice, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, funk, rock
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, purple, blue, red
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 2. the fan classical is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
 5. the person drinking juice is not the fan funk##6
 6. the person who likes red is between the person who likes ebony and the person drinking fanta##2
 7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking fanta and the fan electronic##2
 9. the fan funk is somewhere to the right of the fan classical##5
10. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job           | juice  | mirinda    | fanta | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | classical | rock     | funk       |
| Sport         | ebony   | red    | purple     | blue   |

