.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, fishing, woodworking
House: palace, craftsman, gothic-revival, townhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, writer, security-guard
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the townhouse house##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the townhouse house and the palace house##2
3. the palace house is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the software-developer is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the security-guard is between the nurse and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking  | fishing  | cooking  | baking    |
| Movie-Genre   | palace       | craftsman   | townhouse | gothic-revival |
| Sport         | writer | nurse | security-guard   | software-developer    |

