.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, hedgehog, bird
City: miami, prague, marseilles, berlin
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, van
 1. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to berlin is not the owner of the bird##6
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the owner of the bird is between the person traveling to prague and the person driving the van##2
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
 6. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
 8. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
10. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |       2       |     3      |     4     |
| Food        | snake     | hedgehog   | bird | rat    |
| Job         | marseilles | berlin | miami | prague |
| Transport   | bike            | van           | bus        | subway    |

