4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the modern house is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
7. the person watching superhero movies is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking juice##2
8. the palace house is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
