.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, lily, marigold
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, september, june, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person drinking milk##6
 4. the person who growslily is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person drinking milk is not the person who growslily##6
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 8. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
10. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
11. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | 7up     | mirinda    | milk       | sprite |
| Sport       | marigold | orchid   | daffodil | lily  |
| Transport   | september | june | february   | may |

