1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the palace house##6
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the palace house is on the far left##1
9. the art-deco house is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |   3   |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | juice | soy-milk   |
| Food       | palace   | gothic-revival        | art-deco | cottage    |
