.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, tea, coffee
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo, blend, swisher
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hedgehog, rat
 1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the cat and the swisher-smoker##2
 3. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 5. the owner of the rat is not the game-smoker##6
 6. the person drinking coffee is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the person drinking juice is not the owner of the rat##6
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
10. the game-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3       |     4     |
| Food   | coffee    | juice       | tea          | water |
| Job    | tiparillo | blend | swisher | game |
| Pet    | cat       | hedgehog   | rat           | goldfish  |

