 5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the fan jazz##2
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is between the fan folk and the fan hip-hop##2
 8. the fan hip-hop is not the person watching epic movies##6
 9. the fan d&b is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |     3     |        4        |
